"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-4-2-singapores-only-olympic-gold-medallist-joseph-schooling-retires\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Schooling stunned the world when he beat Michael Phelps for the 100m butterfly gold at the Rio Olympics in 2016.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.617377671628532e-41, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Joseph Schooling, the swimmer who won Singapore's first and to date only Olympic gold medal in 2016, has announced his retirement from the pool at the age of 28.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joseph Schooling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joseph_Schooling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known in the city-state as \\\"Singapore's Flying Fish\\\", Schooling stunned the swimming world when he beat his boyhood hero Michael Phelps to win the 100 metres butterfly with a time of 50.39 seconds at the Rio Olympics.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.8428444768007701, \"rank\": 0.18645836807722693, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.617377671628532e-41, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the American swimming legend Phelps's last individual race of his career and came after Phelps won a record eight gold medals at the London Olympics in 2012.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999473167526178, \"rank\": 5.223730398754852e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999744522942, \"rank\": 2.55463323087778e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999744522942, \"rank\": 2.55463323087778e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.963792981324553, \"rank\": 0.03712943144251645, \"text\": \"London Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schooling found it difficult to match that level of global success after 2016, winning a solitary bronze medal at the 2017 world championships and crashing out in the heats in his title defence at the 2021 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today marks the beginning of a new chapter - I will be retiring from competitive swimming,\\\" he said in a message posted on Facebook on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 1042, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It comes a time when everyone has to flip the page, turn a new chapter.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my time to do that, this is my official retirement,\\\" Schooling said.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are no regrets.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am filled with gratitude for every experience that swimming has brought into my life.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The victories were exhilarating, the defeats humbling, and together, they have forged a resilience in me that I will carry forward into my next chapter.\\\"\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The defeats have been more frequent than the victories in the eight years since Rio but Schooling will retire with three Asian Games gold medals and 29 from the Southeast Asian Games.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999996825863, \"rank\": 3.173856589565781e-10, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998771038539, \"rank\": 1.2289618099808521e-07, \"text\": \"Southeast Asian Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southeast_Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schooling holds eight Singapore records, six in individual events and two in the relays.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.8428444768007701, \"rank\": 0.18645836807722693, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, Schooling was forced to apologise for using cannabis in Vietnam while competing there on leave from military service.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7596369381689343, \"rank\": 0.21752983286876826, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schooling was left out of the Singapore team for last year's delayed Asian Games in Hangzhou because two other swimmers had recorded faster times.\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.8428444768007701, \"rank\": 0.18645836807722693, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 1949, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 2.7212750457932174e-12, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told the Straits Times it was \\\"a bummer\\\" and that he was undecided about his future heading into another Olympic year.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While I am stepping away from competing, swimming will forever be a part of who I am.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has given me a platform to inspire others to chase their dreams, no matter the odds,\\\" he added on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am eager to explore new passions, face different challenges, and see where this next phase of life takes me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": []}]}"